      <div class="msgContentFrame">You can macro these with /eaction &lt;slot#&gt; &quot;Ability Name&quot;. <br /> <br />So: <br />/eaction 1 &quot;Preserve&quot; <br />/eaction 2 &quot;Hasty Hand&quot; <br /> <br />This will put them in the appropriate ability slots, and won't overwrite your action bars.</div>
